              <div class="roadmap-node"></div>
              <div class="roadmap-content">
                <h3>Liquid v2 Animations</h3>
                <p>Enhancing the visual experience with advanced liquid animations that create a unique, immersive interface.</p>
                <ul class="roadmap-features">
                  <li>WebGL fluid simulations</li>
                  <li>Interactive particle effects</li>
                  <li>Scroll-based transformations</li>
                  <li>Liquid cursor effects</li>
                </ul>
